\id 2TH - Margi Tiwi Ənga Tǝm [mfm]
\h Tasalonika Nǝ Mǝthlǝu
\toc3 Tas Mǝth
\toc2 Tasalonika Nǝ Mǝthlǝu
\toc1 Tsǝfǝ Nǝ Bulusu Anǝ Njir Tasalonika Nǝ Mǝthlǝu
\mt2 Cama Tsǝtsǝfǝ Nǝ Bulusu Nǝ Mǝthlǝu Anǝ
\mt1 Njir Tasalonika
\c 1
\s1 Usa Dzau
\p 
\v 1 Cama tsǝtsǝfǝ kǝ sara ara Bulusu, ǝnga Silasu, ba ǝnga Timathlawusu.
\p A nda nǝ daɓǝ dzǝ njir nu kǝra wu mǝlmǝ Tasalonika, kǝra nǝ Hyal Dǝrmǝn ǝnga Thlagǝ Yesu Kǝrsiti.
\p 
\v 2 Bǝgǝ mayiwakur ǝnga huɗǝ pǝrtǝu sara ara Hyal Tada ǝnga Thlagǝ Yesu Kǝrsiti nda nggya ǝnga hyi.
\s1 Lǝ Usaku Ənga Kǝdi Hyal
\p 
\v 3 Kakal nga nyi ˈya na usaku anǝ Hyal cumu aga hyi, nahyi wazha ama, ara mbǝrsar hyi a vǝr cakǝ gagaɗau, ǝnga yiwu kǝra hya vǝr yiwu kǝrhyi a vǝr cakau.
\v 4 Agabangau, ˈya vǝr ɓwasau ǝnga hyi wu daɓǝ dzǝ njir nu Hyal pamǝpamǝ arya sǝsǝˈwu sǝ ǝnga mbǝrsar hyi wu patǝr ɗa dzǝ pamǝpamǝu ǝnga nggya dzadzau kǝra hya vǝr sǝsǝˈwuri.
\p 
\v 5 Kalar sǝˈyar kau ca ngǝ cabiya numa nǝ Hyal tsaˈa nga nyi, arya kau nja nda jigǝwa hyi wu njira a ɗari kakal nda gwu tǝlkur Hyal kǝra hya vǝr sa ɓwaɓwatǝ aga nyi.
\v 6 Hyal ndǝ tsapǝ ngau, ju nda kina ǝnga ɓwaɓwatǝ anǝ njira vǝr lǝ ɓwaɓwatǝ anǝ hyi.
\v 7 Ənga tsu, ju nǝ hyi ɓǝlsar, nahyi kǝra a vǝr sa ɓwaɓwatǝ ǝkkǝˈyi naˈya tsu ma Thlagǝ Yesu cabiya kǝr sara dǝmǝlmau wu uˈu mbǝmbau ǝnga waladi nyiˈyar.
\v 8 Ju sa nǝ nyi ɓwaɓwatǝ anǝ njira gǝra sǝn Hyal ǝnga njira piyari nu ndǝshigu nǝ Thlagǝr mǝn Yesu.
\v 9 Ndu nda sa ɓwaɓwatǝ kǝra gǝra kuɗau, ǝnga na ndu nda lari bama Thlagǝu ǝnga kadakadarkur nǝ dǝnama nyi mai.
\v 10 Sǝˈyar kǝ wu nda ɗa, ar pǝcira ji shida, aga nji cicau ndu sa nǝ nyi kadakadarkur, patǝ njira hǝnggǝri ndu nda gǝnggǝr nyi sǝli. Ənggau, patǝ ǝkkǝˈyi nahyi, ara a hǝnggǝr hyi ǝnga sakida kǝra ˈyi nar hyi.
\p 
\v 11 Ənga najaka sǝ a wu kǝr, ˈya vǝr kǝdi Hyal anǝ hyi cumu, aga Hyalǝr mǝn ja jigǝwa hyi wu ngga nyi, ǝnga dǝnama nyi nga ju nda nyabiya kalar sǝ mǝnahǝ kǝra hyi mǝl ǝnga kalar sǝra ɗǝfuwa hyi nǝr hyi lagur mbǝrsar hyi.
\v 12 ˈYa vǝr kǝdi Hyal kau, aga nja nǝ nyi kadakadarkur anǝ thlǝmǝ Thlagǝr mǝn Yesu wu hyi, ǝnga nahyi tsu, hyu uya kadakadarkur wu ja. Sǝ kǝ wu ɗar kǝr lagur mayiwakur nǝ Hyalǝr mǝn ǝnga Thlagǝ Yesu Kǝrsiti.
\c 2
\s1 Ndǝr Hyaˈa Hangǝkal
\p 
\v 1 Ar kǝra shilǝr Thlagǝr mǝn Yesu Kǝrsiti ǝnga sa ɓǝr mǝn papatǝu ǝkkǝˈyi ja, ˈya vǝr kǝdi hyi wazha ama,
\v 2 a sara hya gǝrahǝ wu ɗǝfuwa hyi kusakusa mai alaga hangǝkala hyi a hyaˈari mai, abǝr pǝcir shilir Thlagǝu a kuɗa shiliri mai. Ma vanyi, abǝr vanyi ndǝ a nar hyi ri abangau, lagur ndǝr haha, alaga cama tsǝtsǝfau, alaga ndǝr papahǝu, alaga nja na abǝr cama ngau sara ara ˈya.
\v 3 A sara hya piyari kalar ndau a nggutana hyi alaga abari mai, ara pǝci ta aˈyi shili mai, kǝl ma gǝra nggandǝrkur kǝ ɗa kwatahǝu, ǝnga ma ndǝr hyaˈa hangǝkal ta cabiya dzau, naja ngǝ ndǝra nji fiya nyi aga sa.
\v 4 Naja ngǝ ndǝra wu tsamǝ kǝrnyi ǝnga kadakadarkur, ju nda pari kalar sǝra nju ngga ǝnga Hyal, ǝnga kalar sǝr dlǝvau. Ju nda fiya kǝrnyi ar vir nggya wu ki Hyal, ǝnga ju fiya kǝrnyi ar viya Hyal.
\p 
\v 5 Nahyi aˈyi a ɗǝngari wa, yu na sǝˈyar kau anǝ hyi ar pǝcira mǝn ar vira zǝmǝu?
\v 6 Kabangǝkau a sǝn hyi sǝra a vǝr kar nyi, aga kǝl ma pǝci nyi a ɗari nga ja dzǝgwa cabiya dzau.
\v 7 Ara ndǝr hyaˈa hangǝkal kǝ a vǝr mǝl thlǝr ɗǝɗǝwa kabangǝkau, a nggyar ja ɗǝɗǝwa kǝl ma ndǝra vǝr kar nyi ara biyar babal kǝ ɓana dzau.
\v 8 Ba ndǝr hyaˈa hangǝkal ka dzǝgwa cabiya dzau, ndǝra Thlagǝu Yesu wu nda tsiya nyi ǝnga sǝ pi sara wu miya ja, ǝnga ja dzǝgwa wushina nyi ǝnga kadakadarkur nǝ shili nyi.
\v 9 Ndǝr hyaˈa hangǝkal kau, ju nda shili ǝnga dǝnama sara ara shatan, ja dzǝgwa sana liya nji ǝnga mǝl sǝ dǝdǝgur ǝnga mǝtsam pampamǝu.
\v 10 Ənga ja nda nggutana njira ar lagu sasa ǝnga kalar sǝ ɗǝmwaˈyi kǝra wu sǝkwa dzau, ara ndǝ piyari yiwu jiri kǝra wu nda kǝtiya nda.
\v 11 Arya najaka sǝ ngǝ Hyal a nda shabiya hangǝkala nda aga nda hǝnggǝr ǝnga fatiya nyi,
\v 12 aga abangǝ nju nda thlana nda numa patǝu, ara na ndǝ hǝnggǝri ǝnga jirkur mai, ama ndǝ yiwu ɗǝmwaˈyikur.
\s1 Hya Nggya Ənga Jirkur
\p 
\v 13 Kakal nga nyi ˈya lǝ usaku anǝ Hyal cumu arya hyi, nahyi wazha ama kǝra Thlagǝ a yiwu, ara Hyal ngǝ caɗǝbiya hyi aga hya ɗa wu nji tanggǝrma kǝra uya mbǝɗǝ lagur Mambǝl, ca ngǝ mǝliya hyi cici ǝnga lagur hǝnggǝri wu jiri.
\v 14 Aga kǝ nga ji ngga hyi, lagur ndǝshigu ˈya kǝra ˈyi nǝ hyi, aga hya uya kadakadarkur nǝ Thlagǝr mǝn Yesu Kǝrsiti.
\v 15 Agabangau, wazha ama, hya ciya dzau ǝnga hya sǝɓiya highiɓǝ ˈyar kǝ ˈyi nǝ hyi kau, alaga ǝnga miya ba lagur cama tsǝtsǝfau.
\p 
\v 16 Bǝgǝ Thlagǝr mǝn Yesu Kǝrsiti ǝnga kǝrnyi ba Hyal Tada, kǝra cabiya mǝn yiwukur, ja nǝ mǝn tsǝtsǝku ɗǝfu kǝra gǝra kuɗau ǝnga fǝr kǝr mǝnahǝu.
\v 17 Bǝgǝ ja nǝ hyi tsǝtsǝku ɗǝfu, ǝnga ja nǝ hyi dǝnama wu patǝr sǝ mǝnahǝu kǝra hyu mǝl ǝnga sǝra hyu na.
\c 3
\s1 Bulusu Wu Yiwu Nja Kǝdi Hyal Anǝ Nda
\p 
\v 1 Wu jomǝya nyi, wazha ama, ˈya vǝr kǝdi aga hya kǝdi Hyal anǝ ˈya. Hya kǝdi Hyal aga ndǝshigu nǝ Thlagǝu a tǝtǝlnakǝr kusakusa, ǝnga aga ja ɗa ǝnga kadakadarkur, ǝnggǝr kǝra ji shili anǝ hyi.
\v 2 Ənga tsu hya kǝdi Hyal, aga nja kǝtiya ˈya ara nji ɗǝmwaˈyu ǝnga nji shishi, ara aˈyi kalar nji ngǝ ǝnga mbǝrsa mai.
\v 3 Ama Thlagǝ ndǝ tsaˈa miya ɗǝfu ngau, ju nda nǝ hyi dǝnama, ǝnga ja kǝtiya hyi ara nji ɗǝmwaˈyu.
\v 4 A mbǝrsar ˈya ǝnga Thlagǝu abǝr hya vǝr mǝl sǝra ˈyi na aga hya mǝl, ǝnga tsu hya dumwa ǝnga mǝl nda.
\v 5 Bǝgǝ Thlagǝu ja tsǝkwar ɗǝfuwa hyi aga hya sǝnbiya yiwukur nǝ Hyal, ǝnga sǝsǝu sǝ lagur Kǝrsiti.
\s1 Mǝl Thlǝr Sǝ Mǝnahǝ Ngau
\p 
\v 6 Wazha ama, ˈya vǝr na anǝ hyi wu thlǝmǝr Thlagǝr mǝn Yesu Kǝrsiti, abǝr hya tǝkǝ ǝnga kalar zamǝ haɗǝwa, ǝnga naja aˈyi wu yiwu mǝl thlǝr ǝnga sǝra hyi highiɓǝri ara ˈya mai.
\v 7 Nahyi ǝnga kǝrhyi, a sǝn hyi ǝnggǝr kǝra kikyau hya faˈabiya hiya sǝra ˈyi mǝl. Wu pǝcira ˈya ǝgya hyi na ˈya aˈyi nggya dzafǝ mai.
\v 8 Ənga tsu naˈya aˈyi wu sǝm sǝr sǝm nji gǝra kina mai. Ama a sar ˈya ɓwaɓwatǝ vuˈyi ǝnga puci a vǝr mǝl thlǝr, aga ˈya sara ɗa sǝ tǝdǝɓǝ anǝ hyi.
\v 9 Sǝra ɗa ˈyi mǝl abangau, ara aˈyi ˈya gǝra dǝnama nǝ yiwa aga hya dlǝwar ˈya mai, ama aga ˈya ɗa sǝr fǝ li kǝra hyu faˈabiya hiya nyi.
\v 10 Wu pǝcira mǝn ar vira zǝmǝu, a nar hyir ˈya abǝr ma ndǝ nggǝl ara mǝl thlǝr, a sara nja lǝ sǝr sǝm anǝ nyi mai.
\p 
\v 11 ˈYi na abangǝ ara ˈyi nggari abǝr alenyi nji wu hyi, nji haɗǝwa ngau, thlǝr mǝl aˈyi ara nda mai, kǝl nggya aga jiɓa njir mǝl thlǝr.
\v 12 Culi najaka nji ˈya vǝr tǝɗǝ himiya nda ǝnga nǝ nda sǝr ɓǝla wu dǝnama nǝ Thlagǝ Yesu Kǝrsiti aga nda mǝliya kǝrnda, nda mǝl thlǝr aga nda uya ɗǝfǝ kǝra nda sǝm.
\v 13 Nahyi tsu, wazha ama, a sara hya hǝɗa ǝnga mǝl sǝra tsaˈa mai.
\p 
\v 14 Kalar ndǝra nggǝl ara nu sǝra ˈyi nana a gwar cama tsǝtsǝfǝ kau, hya fǝr li mǝnahǝu ar ja. A sara hya daɓǝr kǝr ǝnga ja mai, aga ja gu sǝli.
\v 15 Ama a sara hya fiya nyi ar viya dawa mai, ama hya tǝɗǝ himiya ja ar viya zǝr ama.
\s1 Fǝ Barka
\p 
\v 16 Bǝgǝ Thlagǝ ǝnga kǝrnyi ndǝr lǝ huɗǝ pǝrtǝu, ja nǝ hyi huɗǝ pǝrtǝ cumu wu kalar lagu. Bǝgǝ Thlagǝ ja nggya ǝnga hyi patǝu.
\v 17 Nayi Bulusu ngǝ tsǝfǝ najaka usa dzau ǝnga tsa yau. Kǝ ngǝ sakida nǝ kalar cama tsǝtsǝfǝ ɗa. Ənggǝr kǝ nga yu tsǝfau.
\v 18 Bǝgǝ mayiwakur nǝ Thlagǝr mǝn Yesu Kǝrsiti ja nggya ǝnga hyi patǝu. Amina.
